rComments: Lots of reading and writing assignment in his class. Makes sure you read all assigned reading before the class. Honestly, if you don't read those stuffs, the atmosphere of this class could be very embarrassing because nobody knows what to say.

If you're looking for a two hour nap in the middle of the week his class is perfect. Assignments are pointless and he gives quizzes on maps so its easy marks. If you don't do the readings and talk in class, good luck.
